    • Constructor Detail

      • AppTheme

        public AppTheme​(java.lang.String primaryDark,
                java.lang.String primaryLight,
                java.lang.String secondaryDark,
                java.lang.String contrastDark,
                java.lang.String contrastLight)
        Overrides default specified in DefaultThemeValue value with those passed as parameter.
        Parameters:
        primaryDark - the new color for the parameter in the form '#HHHHHH' where H is anan haxidecimal character. Opacity will be 1.
        primaryLight - the new color for the parameter in the form '#HHHHHH' where H is anan haxidecimal character. Opacity will be 1.
        secondaryDark - the new color for the parameter in the form '#HHHHHH' where H is anan haxidecimal character. Opacity will be 1.
        contrastDark - the new color for the parameter in the form '#HHHHHH' where H is anan haxidecimal character. Opacity will be 1.
        contrastLight - the new color for the parameter in the form '#HHHHHH' where H is anan haxidecimal character. Opacity will be 1.
